column5: We're leaving in about an hour... see ya all there!!  Daves seminar series.  Seminar location.  Its gunna be fun!!!  FREE Subs and cards!!
Oh ya... wear your OFC hats if ya got them.. if ya dont ill bring some with me!!
I'll see ya there! You can sell me a hat @ the show.
We's a be goin too, eh.
I'm showering right after this post and gonna be on my way!
Were HERE!!!   Quick bite and the doors open at 6:30!!
Well I hope that everyone took advantage of these nights as they are great and you will have a great time out there heck free Sub Way and a $10 gift card also cool.
